family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>图4 热红外无人机勘测研究区域温度数据</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"></span></p><h1 style=\"white-space: normal; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; font-size: 32px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #FFC000; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">绩效评价</span></h1><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">1.安全韧性效益评价</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">水安全-自然岸线保有率（%）</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">P<sub>Shore</sub>=A<sub>Natural</sub>/A<sub>River</sub></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">式中：P<sub>Shore</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">为自然岸线保有率，A<sub>Natural</sub>为重要河湖自然岸线长度，A<sub>River</sub>为河湖水系岸线总长度。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221024/5b6e5b458b85f102994e75cb26c551f4.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"395\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 395px; width: 800px;\"/></span><br/></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图5 自然岸线保有率</strong></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">结果表明，2020年正定镇场地生态岸线长度达33.3km，在生态建设后，正定镇自然岸线保有率由2015年的47.5%提升至92.3%，同比增长了44.8%，增加了12.6km的生态岸线，创造了自然的河道风景，提升了生态绿化滨水界面的生境多样性。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">水安全-树木拦截雨水总量</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">通过ENVI对2020年正定镇worldview遥感影像进行波段计算，获得场地NDVI指数分布，再反演得到叶面积指数分布。另通过调研实地样方，获得植被激光雷达数据，通过点云分割得到群落类型及分布，依照不同群落类型进行样方截留雨水径流效益计算。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">最后通过建立样方叶面积指数与截留雨水径流能力回归方程，推导正定镇滹沱河生态景观拦截雨水径流生态效益。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/9c296f40ba65802c5436713c66f1de6f.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"432\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 432px; width: 800px;\"/></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图6 树木拦截雨水总量</strong></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">结果表明，场地滞留雨水径流生态效益与乔木栽植密度高度相关，落叶阔叶林拦截雨水效益高于常绿针叶林。正定镇场地平均拦截雨水径流能力120.15kg/m²·年，其中奥体公园、子龙码头、艺术生态岛3处场地拦截雨水效益较好，而格林小镇度假村的拦截效益较差，为10 9.07kg/m²·年。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2.生态调节效益评价</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">植被保护与修复-植被覆盖率</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">NDVI=(NIR-RED)/(NIR+RED)</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">式中：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">其中NDVI为表征植被覆盖率的植被归一化指数，NIR为近红外波段的反射值；RED为红光波段的反射值。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/05ff5ca8df05e41bc7b8597b52e44542.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"448\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 448px;\"/></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图7&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">2015年2020年间植被覆盖率变化分析图</strong></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">结果表明，正定镇平均植被覆盖度为61.9%，整体相较2015年提升62.9%。通过栽植树木，转变裸地荒地为绿地使大部分场地的植被覆盖度显著提升；奥体公园、叠翠山公园现状覆盖度较高，而滹沱花海、格林小镇度假村植被覆盖度较低。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">植被保护与修复-植物群落生长情况</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">依据场地遥感影像，识别场地现状植物群落的位置并判断场地不同类型绿地占比。</span></p><br/><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/c45ef993f05783ad6952ff312ae4084b.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"451\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 451px;\"/><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图8&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>植物群落生长情况分析图</strong></strong></span></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">结果表明，依据正定镇2020年11月的多光谱遥感影像对植被类型进行解译。场地内针阔叶林总体比例达到37%，高于30%，能够产生生态效益。其中，针叶林占场地整体植物植被覆盖的9%，阔叶林占28%，草地占42%，湿地占8%，苗圃占13%。除表格标红的区域外，其他区域均实现了乔木净覆盖率30%以上。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><strong>碳存储与封存——植被固碳能力</strong></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">使用CASA模型计算植物净初级生产力(NPP)表征植被固碳能力</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"></span>。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/618b9ad62414d4ad56d46064bc118053.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"452\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 452px;\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图10&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><strong>2015年-2020年间植被固碳能力变化分析图</strong></strong></span></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">结果表明，正定镇的年平均植被生产力为136.57 gC/m2·年。映秀山公园、滹沱湿地、滹沱印记、明曦湖公园西侧的植被固碳能力较高。相较于2015年映秀山公园、滹沱印记、滹沱花海植被净初级生产力提升较多，转变农田为丰富的植物群落，提升区域的碳汇能力。奥体公园、星野公园以及叠翠山公园存在将苗圃转化为疏林草地与未栽植树木的公园，导致相应区域储碳能力下降。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">3.生物多样性效益评价</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">栖息地创建、保护和恢复-代表物种生境面积占比</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">P<sub>Biology</sub>=S<sub>Biology</sub>/S<sub>Habitat</sub></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">式中：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">其中是P<sub>Biology</sub>代表物种生境面积占比，S</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><sub>Biology</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">为指一定区域中代表物种的生境面积，S</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><sub>Habitat</sub></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">为评价区面积。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/253a0e81d426010bf8335bccaa7f86fa.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"461\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 461px;\"/></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图11&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>代表物种生境面积占比分析图</strong></strong></span></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">结果表明，正定镇物种生境面积占比约为20.1%，其中艺术生态岛、叠翠山公园、滹沱花海、奥体公园食源或栖息地丰富，兼具林地裸地疏林草地多种生境，适宜多种林鸟和水鸟生存。而水上世界、胜利大街花海、格林小镇度假村由于距离公路过近，场地植被覆盖度差，植被种类较为单一，不能满足大多数鸟类栖息、觅食需求。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">4.健康舒适效益评价</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>景观品质-特色景观设施种类</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">实地调研特色景观设施，包括文化设施、体育健身设施、休憩设施种类数量。</span></p><br/><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/ba8709d3cd66933654365340bb8bb5b5.png\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 441px;\" width=\"800\" height=\"441\" alt=\"\"/></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图12&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong>体育休憩设施种类及数量分析图</strong></span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/d53bfc8bbc5cdd6e551e823ce7f54673.png\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 441px;\" width=\"800\" height=\"441\" alt=\"\"/></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图13&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>体育健身设施种类及数量分析图</strong></span></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">结果表明，正定镇区域具有约5个主题场所，50个运动场所，80个观景场所，250个休息场所，总面积约86.41公顷，占正定镇区域面积的4.4%，可供约67万人同时进行休憩活动。具有足球场、篮球场、羽毛球场、网球场、户外营地等健身场所，总面积约32.65公顷，占正定镇区域面积的1.7%，可供约1.1万人同时进行健身活动</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">5.创新活力效益评价</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>游憩与社会价值-社会关注度</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">通过社交媒体上报道或评价场地的相关博文、用户名、评论内容、图片内容等信息，通过图片内容提取场地信息，通过文字内容获取地理信息，在2020年worldview-3遥感影像上进行空间匹配，得出社交媒体信息空间分布，利用arcgis软件对空间点进行核密度分析，得出场地热点区域分布，根据场地内容信息和热点区域分布获得要素关注度的分析结果。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/2a0ce97e769ef915bff9f7e0b63052ce.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"451\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 451px;\"/></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图14&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 11px;\"><strong><strong>社会关注度分析图</strong></strong></span></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">结果表明，从热点的地区的空间分布来看，正定镇热点地区分布，明曦湖公园、滹沱花海、城市轨迹、滹沱之舞等公园较高，星野公园、叠翠山公园较低。红线外围的正定古城区域也吸引了一定数量的游客，与滹沱河一期流域呈联动作用。</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>绿色低碳-低碳建设节约效益</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">P<sub>CO2</sub>=a*K<sub>Car</sub>*L</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">式中：</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">P<sub>CO2</sub>为场地减少的碳排放量，a为碳排放标准系数，场地内外同时段平均车流量K<sub>Car</sub>，L为场地道路长度。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221112/564af0d78ea104087516840225fe1722.png\" width=\"800\" height=\"463\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 463px;\"/></p><h5 style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图15&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><strong>低碳建设节约效益分析图</strong></strong></span></h5><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">结果表明，场地通过建设公园，限制车流量，倡导游人绿色出行，减少场地交通所产生碳排放量。结合碳排放系数数据与车辆行驶距离，计算得出通过公园建设减少碳排放量为3.94kg CO<sup>2</sup>/车。同一时间所观测到公园外部车流量为753辆/h，公园内部道路同一时间段内部车流量为209辆/h。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 0em;\"><br/></p>',1665296299,1668238421,'0','0','0'),(103,1,2,'江苏省南京市江宁区黄龙岘村',320000,320100,320115,'江苏省/南京市/江宁区','80.11',15,'/uploads/20221022/7ee29e9e23d82aa8c66fcd710a775fd6.png','黄龙岘村位于南京市江宁区江宁街道牌坊社区，紧邻西部生态旅游环线，南接337省道，村庄东邻战备水库、西接牌坊水库，交通便利，区位优越。占地80.11公顷，茶园2000多亩。','2021-12-31T16:00:00.000Z','','','ZXGroup','',7,'','美丽乡村建设新模式','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 3em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">区位：</span></strong>南京市江宁区江宁街道牌坊社区<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 3em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">面积：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">80.11公顷</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 3em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">人口：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); line-height: 3em;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">资源：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">茶山、竹林</span></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); font-size: 32px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #FFC000; font-size: 18px;\">村庄概况</span><br/></h1><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">黄龙岘村位于南京市江宁区江宁街道牌坊社区，紧邻西部生态旅游环线，南接337省道，村庄东邻战备水库、西接牌坊水库，交通便利，区位优越。占地80.11公顷，茶园2000多亩。黄龙岘为典型的丘陵山水田园乡村，四周茶山、竹林环绕，黄龙潭当立其中，景色秀美，资源丰富，如图1。黄龙岘村属于丘陵山地，四周茶山、竹林环绕。主产的黄龙岘“龙毫、龙针”茶叶精采细摘、手工制作，茶香四溢、口味醇厚，获得2009年南京市“雨花杯”银奖，2015年“交建杯”金奖，深受民众的喜爱。是“金陵茶村”都市生态休闲旅游示范村，素有“金陵茶文化休闲旅游第一村”的美誉，是江宁区确定的新一批“金花村”之一。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <img width=\"541\" height=\"363\" src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221115/a742efda3e7504606a4f9ec8153de81d.jpg\" style=\"background: url(&quot;/assets/addons/ueditor/i18n/zh-cn/images/localimage.png&quot;) center center no-repeat; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); width: 541px; height: 363px;\" alt=\"undefined\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图1 黄龙岘村平面图</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><br/></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><h1 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); font-size: 32px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);\"><span style=\"color: #FFC000; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;\">评价概况</span><br/></h1><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">针对黄龙岘村进行生态景观营造模式与生态景观绩效评价研究，调研方法包括三个环节：①基于地理信息技术手段采集示范点景观空间数据；②对管理者、村民、游客开展访谈，收集示范点空间使用意见；③结合村镇景观绩效评价关键因子与量化计算模型，验证修正景观绩效评价体系。实地调研走访流程，如图2。</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221116/c24811214242358984ff01c493ec58d7.png\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图2 实地调研走访流程</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">黄龙岘村业态分布完善，有茶馆、饭店、民宿、超市、体验馆、党员活动中心等场所，涵盖了文化活动、餐饮购物、民宿体验等类型，工作日平均人流量80人/小时，周末平均人流量430人/小时，旅游旺季平均人流量1020人/小时，人流量统计表如图7；黄龙岘村建设中多处使用乡土元素，地面青石板、毛石、碎石、原木铺装、乡土特色建筑等塑造了传统宜人的特色景观风貌。村内有多处开放公共空间、滨水空间，如黄龙阁、黄龙大茶馆等，提供了完善的游憩设施，打造了美丽的乡村风貌。除村镇建设用地及道路外，整体生境质量良好，茶园、晏湖周围生境质量相对较高，具有重要的生物多样性保护价值，对构建完整的生态多样性体系具有积极的环境条件。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><h1 style=\"white-space: normal; font-size: 32px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; color: #FFC000;\">绩效评价</span></h1><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 3em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">1.安全韧性效益评价</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0in; white-space: normal; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:120%\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:120%\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 120%;\">地质安全——土壤侵蚀量</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">土壤侵蚀量（t·hm-2a-1）=降雨侵蚀力因子（MJ·mm·hm-2·h-1·a-1）×土壤可侵蚀性因子×坡长因子×生物因子×工程措施因子×耕作措施因子。使用GIS数据分析平台进行空间分析与计算，得到黄龙岘村土壤侵蚀量分析图，图3。结果表明黄龙岘村水土流失整体面积较小，主要分布在地势较高、远离村镇的区域，村镇建设用地水土流失不明显。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221116/34e95a593d4c2c20278608c5d06f3c74.png\" width=\"509\" height=\"307\" style=\"width: 509px; height: 307px;\"/></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 28px; line-height: 120%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 120%;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 120%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 120%;\">图3 黄龙岘村土壤侵蚀量分析图</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 120%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 120%;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 120%;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; line-height: 120%; font-size: 14px;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong>农田景观完整性</strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">通过fragstats软件计算PROXIM指标，度量同类型拼块间的邻近程度以及景观的破碎度，如值小，表明同类型拼块间离散程度高或景观破碎程度高；值大，表明同类型拼块间邻近度高，景观完整性好。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">结果表明，黄龙岘村整体农田景观风貌较好，龙坊路北侧茶田较南部茶缘阁茶田更为完整连续，如图4。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221116/453f9440c2aa5b83e41a71ece1dd0f83.png\" width=\"533\" height=\"407\" style=\"width: 533px; height: 407px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图4 黄龙岘村农田景观风貌完整性分析图</span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 3em\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">2.生态调节效益评价</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0in;white-space: normal;direction: ltr;unicode-bidi: embed;text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em\"><br/></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 28px;white-space: normal;line-height: 19.2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size: 14px\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 16.8px\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: left; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #0D0D0D; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;\">碳存储与封存-植被固碳能力</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size: 14px\">现状总固碳量约266196.9kg/年。除村域中心区域外，其余地区以松林、竹林、阔叶林表现最佳，如图5。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221116/e736cae7e9fc593e122d3e9f8712d906.jpg\" width=\"562\" height=\"403\" style=\"width: 562px; height: 403px;\"/></span><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图5 黄<strong>龙岘村植被固碳能力分析图</strong></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 3em\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑\">3.生物多样性</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0in;white-space: normal;direction: ltr;unicode-bidi: embed;text-indent: 2em;line-height: 2em\"><br/></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 28px;white-space: normal;line-height: 19.2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;;font-size: 14px\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;white-space: normal;direction: ltr;unicode-bidi: embed;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;color: #0D0D0D;font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px\"></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:28px;line-height:120%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 120%;\">栖息地创建、保护和恢复——生境质量</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">运用InVEST3.8.9模型中评估生态环境质量的子模块——生境质量评估模块对黄龙岘村进行生境质量的定量评估。模型处理所需数据包括：当前的土地利用数据、生境对威胁的敏感性、生境与威胁之间的距离，以及受保护的程度。结果表明，除村镇建设用地及道路周边区域，整体生境质量良好，其中，茶缘阁、晏公湖周围生境质量相对较高，如图6。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;line-height: 2em;text-indent: 2em\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221116/31b63900379486de23c4e930516a2947.png\" width=\"561\" height=\"384\" style=\"width: 561px; height: 384px;\"/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">图6&nbsp;<strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\">黄<strong>龙岘村生境质量分析图</strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 12px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\