YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><br/><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; text-align: left; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #FFC000; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>村庄概况</strong></span><br/></h1><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">常口村位于福建省将乐县东部、闽江支流金溪河畔，与省道204线毗邻，距县城15公里。村域面积13.83平方公里，其中耕地0.12万亩，林地1.9万亩。常口村依山傍水，全村森林覆盖率超过90%，如图1所示。该村先后获得全国文明、省级园林式庄生态乡振兴示范村等称号。\r\n截至2018年底，全村共有246户，常住人口792人。主要产业包括特色农业（脐橙、芙蓉李、烟叶等）、乡村旅游（云衢山漂流）等。常口村以金溪及周边地区为生态基底，以水系与路网为廊道，统筹山水林田湖各要素，具有较好的景观风貌本底。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221021/483ed09d5a3c2cf11e706726bc86896b.jpg\" width=\"698\" height=\"613\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 698px; height: 613px;\"/></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\">图1 常口村平面图</span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;\"></strong></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;\"></strong></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2;\"><br/></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; text-align: left; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; color: #FFC000; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>评价概况</strong></span></h1><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 0em;\">针对常口村进行生态景观营造模式与生态景观绩效评价研究，调研方法包括三个环节：①基于地理信息技术手段采集示范点景观空间数据；②对管理者、村民、游客发放问卷、开展访谈，收集示范点空间使用意见；③结合村镇景观绩效评价关键因子与量化计算模型，验证修正景观绩效评价体系。实地调研走访流程，如图2。</span><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 2; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221021/9854049d4cb940944b1e2a61508c5717.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"184\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 800px; height: 184px;\"/></strong></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">图2 实地调研走访流程</span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 120%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;\"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><br/></p><h1 style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding: 0px 4px 0px 0px; text-align: left; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px; color: #FFC000;\"><strong>绩效评价</strong></span></h1><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">1.安全韧性效益评价</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">地质安全-地质灾害易发性</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">使用GIS软件-空间分析工具计算：a=b×0.3+c×0.2+d×0.25+e×0.15+f×0.1</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">式中：a——地质灾害易发性指数；b——岩石风化程度系数坡度；c——坡度；d——岩石风化程度，岩石风化程度系数为：未风化，0.9-1.0；微风化，0.8-0.9；中风化，0.4-0.8；强风化，＜0.4；e——植被盖度；f——降雨因子</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 25px; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; line-height: 2;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221021/7ca994c9e4b6eb095c42594b8667594f.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"195\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 195px;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;\"><strong>图3 地质安全评价结果图</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 120%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">常口村核心区域地形平坦，地质安全系数高，靠近后山区域坡度较大，地质安全系数相对较低，应保持村庄与山体之间的缓冲距离，限制山体过度开发；地质安全系数较低处，应设置护坡，以避免山体滑坡。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; white-space: normal; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">水文安全-雨水拦截总量</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; white-space: normal; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">使用国家树木效益计算器计算：Q=Σqi·Ni</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">式中：Q——树木拦截雨水总量（m3）；qi——i类树种单棵树木雨水拦截量（m3/棵）；Ni——i类树种数量（棵）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221024/b2bec74de9e079c40c622fe11f8db717.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 234px;\" width=\"400\" height=\"234\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221024/6983c054f3f812955d4e28fd746211f6.jpg\" width=\"255\" height=\"234\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 255px; height: 234px;\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\">图4 雨水拦截总量评价结果图&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图5 各类树种数量和总雨水拦截量</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 16.8px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">常口村核心区域地形平坦，靠近后山区域以及常兴湖绿地雨水拦截量较大，建成后场地每年雨水拦截总量为92立方米。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"line-height: 3em;\"><strong style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2.生态调节效益评价</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; white-space: normal; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">碳存储与封存-植被固碳能力</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\">评价方式：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\">使用国家树木效益计算器计算：R=Σri·Ni</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\">式中：R——树木固碳总量（吨/年）；ri——i类树种单棵树木年固碳量（吨/棵·年）；Ni——i类树种数量（棵）</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221024/d8052a6872b00a85d9e47058b07343ec.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 229px;\" width=\"400\" height=\"229\" alt=\"\"/>&nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"http://ies-admin.zhuo-zhuo.com/uploads/20221024/d59875fa0677735e3cad5a8b53fd1e50.jpg\" width=\"244\" height=\"229\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 244px; height: 229px;\"/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em; text-align: center;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 32px; white-space: normal; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 12px;\">图6 植被固碳能力评价结果图&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 图7 各类树种数量和总固碳量</strong><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">评价结果：</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 16.8px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px;\">常口村核心区域地形平坦，靠近后山区域、常兴湖绿地以及儿童乐园附近区域固碳量较大，建成后场地每年固碳量为5207.54kg。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; white-space: normal; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; word-break: normal; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 3em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 2em